values: Please post con-crit, comments, suggestions on how I'm playing Bee here! Comments are screened, anon is enabled.

<tt>Audial sensors aren't malfunctioning, then. 

Strange. Very strange.</tt>
<tt>I think the thing I hate the most about this ship is not knowing what's happening at home.</tt>

+++Attempting to access World Wide Web. . .+++ +++Unable to access World Wide Web. . .+++ +++Accessing local network ShipNet. . .+++ +++Access Granted+++ Hello? Is anyone out there? This is Bumblebee, attempting to contact any Autobot in the area. I seem to have been hijacked in some manner by an unknown force. Looking out this porthole, I seem to be onboard an ocean-going transport of some type. No land within visual range. I've also been shrunk. I'm not sure how; as if I need to be smaller than I already was. Honestly... If anyone out there gets this message, please respond.
